rg6.html \u0423\u0433\u043e\u043b\u043e\u043a \u043d\u0435\u0431\u0430]\n<!-- ==External links== -->\n\n{{IFIL aircraft}}\n\n[[Category:1950s Romanian civil trainer aircraft]]\n[[Category:Reghin]]\n", "name_user": "Petebutt", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IFIL-Reghin_RG-6"}
